appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We’re excited to introduce you to the latest version of the Honeywell Connect Mobile app! This update enhances the Variable Air Volume (VAV) Balancing feature.

Here’s what’s new:·       
1. Easy connection over Secure BLE
2. Discovery and balancing of multiple controllers
3. Firmware balancing with simpler configurations and a wizard-style interface 
4. Balancing application logic migrated from legacy Honeywell controllers
5. Multiple balancing methods supported
6. Report generation
